场要说法，但事情并未得到妥善解决。 11 月 28 日下午，《每日经济新闻》记者致电「武汉伟星置业」官微所留电话，对方回应称，「这个事情我们暂时无法对外回复，正在跟（原业主）协商解决，预计有实质性进展后才会对外回复。」 11 月 29 日上午，每经记者电话咨询武汉东湖高新区房管局，询问是否接到相关投诉及处理情况，接听电话的工作人员回复称，已经接到相关业主投诉，已经反馈到市局，事件还在处理中。 11 月 29 日下午，记者了解到，业主代表与开发商进行了第一次协商，开发商的答复是，「原购房业主可赔偿 7.5 折车位优惠券，有效期为 3 个月」。不过部分业主对这一解决方案并不十分认可，认为「这等于在促销车位」。买房不到一年，每平米突然降价超 4000 元！业主「一夜之间损失 50 万」，各方回应来了… | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-83ddc60457fecd2853e8755da6b1ba45_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/632532833"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIsL3a95ji9/tTEAMaCTEwMjg0MTUzOCC0/pyrBjAAONwGQBpyCTYzMjUzMjgzM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1701338931.916167", "card_id": "Q_632628337", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待国产三大 OS 操作系统，这对中国手机厂商来说意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/632628337"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsL3a95ji9/tTEAMaCTEwMjg2Mjc0MSD7z6CrBjAAOC1AG3IJNjMyNjI4MzM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1701338931.916418", "card_id": "Q_630269977", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 67